{"tid":1058730,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"70後社工 遠嫁北方：「普通話 是我常用語言，我是 北京人！」","createTime":"2019-03-12T17:29:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-12T19:39:41.000Z","uid":226548,"like":1,"dislike":46,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"bff646fd50a4d6975be672be2133027c0022c633","tid":1058730,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T17:29:27.000Z","msg":"<ins><a href=\"https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2290645/70後社工移居北京%20覓人生新跑道\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fskypost.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2290645%2F70%E5%BE%8C%E7%A4%BE%E5%B7%A5%E7%A7%BB%E5%B1%85%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%2520%E8%A6%93%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E6%96%B0%E8%B7%91%E9%81%93&d=fcvOs274DMK6OEArnk0LawOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=add6e9b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2290645/70後社工移居北京%20覓人生新跑道</a></ins><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n70後社工周佩儀，02年底到北京旅遊，認識音樂人丈夫，一直留京生活，現有一子一女，並開拓個人事業，十多年來因工作已走遍全國。她坦言學歷不高，能讓自己找到在中國發揮才幹的機遇，慶幸當初決定北上定居。<br />\n<br />\n周佩儀移居北京前，在香港已從事服務復康智障人士的工作逾10年，今天她的工作涉及宏觀的政策倡導，為有需要機構撰寫服務手冊。另外，常要出差各地栽培和督導前綫社工，其服務對象包括智障人士、留守兒童和全國的NGO機構，更會為服務機構撰寫向人大作建議之用的提案。<br />\n<br />\n回想02年因工作遇上樽頸位，她去北京玩兼學普通話，料不到結識了北京男友，二人於05年結婚，她便一直定居北京。「丈夫是自由音樂人，他來香港未必如我能適應北京，故順理成章留下來。」她坦言<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">離港十多年，今天普通話才是她常用語言，並視自己為北京人。<br />\n</span></strong>"},{"pid":"c924ca9d77d4321f796c9a500ff573de409ae0d0","tid":1058730,"uid":38904,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T17:32:33.000Z","msg":"一個社會總有依啲噉嘅垃圾"},{"pid":"cc3f945e9220a9602f4874d0b9a190286e41092d","tid":1058730,"uid":2419,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T17:35:14.000Z","msg":"死上去咪幾好"},{"pid":"7b264c26fc528d5432447c03b47db71cc777789a","tid":1058730,"uid":54876,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T17:38:57.000Z","msg":"上去團聚，算係咁<br />\n好過一車車落黎嘅支畜"},{"pid":"82f0199e60e14bbbda35b7b8a50a622595f55a2f","tid":1058730,"uid":35910,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T17:40:07.000Z","msg":"唔拎特區我唔阻你，成家都唔好拎永世困係支那就最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"857137b3996475aa8ab3a68587f9f04f434145e3","tid":1058730,"uid":35070,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T17:44:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/5/5f/B07.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20061221031658\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F5%2F5f%2FB07.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20061221031658&h=0219c941&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cc02809f6518305f5cab6389cb0b2033f429b49e","tid":1058730,"uid":226955,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T17:46:05.000Z","msg":"她坦言離港十多年，今天普通話才是她常用語言，並<span style=\"color: red;\">視自己為北京人</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係咪想京獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dce021a9f6ece6320a196df070614ebcfbcff800","tid":1058730,"uid":59570,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T17:46:10.000Z","msg":"岩呀，移民去北京講普通話<br />\n<br />\n所以移民黎香港係應該講廣東話"},{"pid":"8f5e0771b448c632410902a2931d82fe3a54fdf9","tid":1058730,"uid":226955,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T17:47:47.000Z","msg":"點解唔叫自己係中國北京人<br />\n反而叫自稱北京人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n京獨鐡證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2d45a248d78b1ac45dfb463f4fc684fd2a2c087","tid":1058730,"uid":184511,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T17:50:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3d74222ced5e9a7fe0674856a3d3fbc3b12a69db","tid":1058730,"uid":57488,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T17:53:25.000Z","msg":"態度正確<br 